@startuml
skinparam style strictuml
hide empty description

state "Idle" as Idle
state "Adding Plant" as Adding
state "Identifying Plant" as Identifying
state "Configuring Plant" as Configuring
state "Connecting Device" as Connecting
state "Assigning Responsibility" as Assigning
state "Saving" as Saving
state "Completed" as Completed
state "Cancelled" as Cancelled

[*] --> Idle

Idle --> Adding : 'Add new plant'\npressed

Adding --> Identifying : Unknown plant type
Adding --> Configuring : Plant type selected

Identifying --> Identifying : Retry identification
Identifying --> Configuring : Type confirmed
Identifying --> Adding : Cancel identification

Configuring --> Connecting : Info filled

Connecting --> Connecting : Try another device
Connecting --> Assigning : Device connected
Connecting --> Assigning : Skip connection

Assigning --> Saving : Confirm adding
Assigning --> Cancelled : Cancel operation

Saving --> Completed : Plant saved\n+ notification sent

Completed --> Idle : Done
Cancelled --> Idle : Return to shared view

Idle --> [*]

@enduml